Thanks for having me so far #EdFringe! Week 2 let’s be having you. 

#empowerment #emotionalhealth #mentalhealthmatters

And the main thing I am feeling is that I have my fricking powers all lined up. I’m in my element.

So bring it on.
The crowds have been laughing, crying, singing and dancing in all the right places, and so have I.
But one thing that i thought would be hard presenting a piece that’s part theatre part rave, celebrating #mentalhealth and #recovery is handling the complex emotions during the actual show itself.
Will I ever get more than 4 hours sleep again?

Here’s my #TruthTuesday: Self producing a 4 week run at the #EdinburghFestival is a huge challenge - are enough tickets going to sell? Are we going to lose thousands of pounds or not? Are any reviewers going to like it? Are any reviewers going to hate it?

BY DAY I'm showing off my mad mouth music skills and empowering the next generation to find their voices in Shlomo’s Beatbox Adventure For Kids
